revisions.rev:
'''Karaurgan''' is a flag stop near the village of Karaurgan in the [[Kars Province]] of [[Turkey]]. The [[Eastern Express]] services the station, operated by the [[Turkish State Railways]], between [[Istanbul]] and [[Kars]].

